BT 1 0 0 1 54 171.6 Tm (about whether gamma oscillations are epiphenomenal or causal. They are neither. They) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 159.6 Tm (are the observable consequence of the phase transition, the way the Meissner effect) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 147.6 Tm (is the observable consequence of superconductivity --- not its cause.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 129.6 Tm (This is why gamma coherence tracks consciousness so precisely: high gamma coherence) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 117.6 Tm (during waking, reduced during deep sleep, abolished under anesthesia, enhanced) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 105.6 Tm (during focused attention. The oscillation tracks the coherence because it IS the) Tj T* ET
