BT 1 0 0 1 54 215.6 Tm (The Libet experiment does not show that free will is an illusion. It shows that) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 203.6 Tm (phase transitions take time.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
