BT 1 0 0 1 54 557.6 Tm (10. What This Framework Does NOT Claim) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 535.6 Tm (Precision matters. This paper makes physical claims. It does not make philosophical) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 523.6 Tm (claims. Specifically:) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 505.6 Tm (1. The framework does not explain WHY coherence produces subjective experience. It) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 493.6 Tm (explains when, where, and how consciousness turns on and off. The hard problem) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 481.6 Tm (remains unsolved. But the hard problem is now constrained to a much smaller space:) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 469.6 Tm (why does coherent neural activity at gamma_c produce experience? This is a better) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 457.6 Tm (question than "why does any information processing produce experience?" because it) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 445.6 Tm (identifies the specific physical conditions.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 427.6 Tm (2. The framework does not claim quantum coherence in the Penrose-Hameroff sense. The) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 415.6 Tm (coherence described here is mesoscopic --- it operates at the scale of neural) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 403.6 Tm (populations \(millions of neurons\), not individual microtubules. Whether quantum) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 391.6 Tm (coherence at the microtubule level contributes to gamma_eff is an empirical) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 379.6 Tm (question. The framework is agnostic on this point. It requires coherence. It does) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 367.6 Tm (not require that the coherence be "quantum" in the Penrose sense.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 349.6 Tm (3. The framework does not claim consciousness is binary. The phase diagram shows a) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 337.6 Tm (continuous variable \(gamma_eff\) controlling a continuous variable \(C\). The) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 325.6 Tm ("transition" at gamma_c is sharp but not discontinuous --- it is the same as the) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 313.6 Tm (superconducting transition, which is a true phase transition but still occurs over a) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 301.6 Tm (narrow range of temperature. Consciousness admits degrees, and those degrees map to) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 289.6 Tm (C values.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 271.6 Tm (4. The framework does not claim to identify all decoherence sources. gamma_eff is an) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 259.6 Tm (effective rate that includes all sources of decoherence in neural tissue ---) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 247.6 Tm (thermal, metabolic, chemical, structural, electromagnetic. The specific) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 235.6 Tm (decomposition of gamma_eff into component sources is an experimental program, not a) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 223.6 Tm (completed theory.) Tj T* ET
.5 w
n 54 209.6 m 558 209.6 l S
