BT 1 0 0 1 54 129.6 Tm (in specific cortical regions should produce feature-specific perceptual unbinding,) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 117.6 Tm (quantitatively predicted by the coherence equation.) Tj T* ET
BT /F3 10 Tf 12 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 99.6 Tm (2. Anesthetic threshold experiment \(Prediction 2\): EEG gamma coherence should show a) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 87.6 Tm (sharp phase-transition signature at loss of consciousness, with the transition point) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 54 75.6 Tm (predictable from baseline coherence.) Tj T* ET
 

